features: 🚗ENTERTAINMENT FOR LONG JOURNEY - Amazing adjustable baby car seat toys and interesting small animals to attract the baby, improve the baby's activity and ability through the baby's play. Make the boring driving time more fun and easy.

🚗SONSORY TOY YOU NEED ON ROAD - This toy can be adjusted in many places so that your baby can easily pinch, touch, and kick the interesting sound accompanied by this toy, which is suitable for babies at different ages.

🚗FINE MOTOR SKILS - Comes with soft Teether, Beads with ring, lion plush with bell, monkey plush with squeaker sound, bird plush with black and white color. They are lovely hanging animal toys which will make interesting sounds to keep the baby busy.

🚗EASY INSTALLATION - We made it very easy for installing the seat in car. Fix the toy under the head restraint of the rear seat of the car through two plastic buckles and two adjusting rods. The length and angle are adjustable to facilitate the baby's play.

🚗PERFECT GIFT TO ENJOY LONG TRIPS - This item is packaged in amazing portable box which is a perfect gift for baby. It is the best baby gift for mom or dad. It will provide safe, fun, and stress-free car travel for families with babies for a long time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Baby enjoys it
reviews.reviewText: I bought this because my 3 month old would scream and cry while we were waiting in the pickup line at my son’s school. I put this toy in my car and my 3 month old enjoys playing with the toys. It doesn’t keep him occupied the entire time we are waiting at the school but it has made the waiting more bearable. It really doesn’t fit in my car with my son’s rear facing infant seat though, it would definitely work better with a child in a forward facing seat but we make it work.

reviews.reviewText: My daughter has hated the car since she was born. Got this when she hit 6 months and we catch her playing with it on longer drives. It stores easily and can rotate the pieces so to her it feels like a new toy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My son was very good in the car, but would get fussy if we weren’t moving. He absolutely loves kicking his feet, so we bought this. Now he will sit in the car for however long and just kick away. The best part is that there is no music playing, which we didn’t want. Just some rattles. It’s a little long (jeep grand Cherokee) but I just tucked the bottom inch behind the car seat base and it’s worked out perfectly

reviews.reviewText: I liked it. I needed something on the cheaper side with the most variety of toy for my baby during a 12 hr round trip car ride. This came in handy and worked well. We even took the toys off and hung them on her stroller so she could play with them that way too.
